# Todo App Architecture

## Tech Stack
-.NET 8
- PostgreSQL
- xUnit
- JWT authentication

## Application Layers
- Presentation: API controllers
- Business: services and repositories
- Data: PostgreSQL database

## Folder Structure
- source/App.Api: API controllers and models
- source/App.Services: services and repositories
- source/App.Data: database context and migrations

## Database or Storage Plan
- PostgreSQL database with EF Core

## Authentication and Authorization Plan
- JWT authentication with roles and permissions